{"tid":917090,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗改了不吃屎]Sony 這招狠!! Xperia XZ4 規格曝光","createTime":"2018-11-26T07:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T18:38:28.000Z","uid":57424,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b788c63f325f70d95955a2e8f1c432eb2cd0c7","tid":917090,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/sony-%E9%80%99%E6%8B%9B%E7%8B%A0-xperia-xz4-%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-083345819.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Fsony-%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%258B%259B%25E7%258B%25A0-xperia-xz4-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-083345819.html&d=CJoisIZfw18%2B85AXPQ5Rqy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=db6a43eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/sony-%E9%80%99%E6%8B%9B%E7%8B%A0-xperia-xz4-%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-083345819.html</a><br />\n<br />\n文章來源：<a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=CJoisIZfw18%2B85AXPQ5Rqy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=117eb176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a><br />\n<br />\nSony 近年發布的產品讓我們有點失望，一是設計上的&ldquo;不足&rdquo;，出現了&ldquo;索半斤&rdquo;&ldquo;肥皂&rdquo;的稱號。對於這些言語，Sony似乎要走偏激的路線來證明自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSony 上任社長平井一夫曾經希望 5G時代的到來，因為希望 Sony 能在5G時代扭轉局勢。伴隨著 5G時代的靠近，相信在下一年，會是 5G時代的競爭，各大手機廠商會爭奇鬥艷。在近期，Sony 曝光了新旗艦 Xperia XZ4 ，它會不會成為 Sony 首款5G手機，加入競爭嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有傳聞 Sony Xperia XZ4 會配備 6.2吋解析度的 OLED 屏幕，屏幕比上一代有提升。性能規格上，將會搭載 7nm Qualcomm Snapdragon 8150 SoC，配以 6GB/8GB RAM+64GB/128GB/256GB儲存。電池容量為4000 mAh ，擁有支援 5G 網絡晶片，意味著 Xperia XZ4 將會支援5G網絡。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝上，會採用 2400萬像素+1600萬像素的雙鏡頭組合。其中1600萬像素鏡頭支援 4K 60fps 影片及960fps 超慢動作，是 Xperia XZ2 Premium 的強化版。<br />\n<br />\n預計 Sony Xperia XZ4 會在2019二月份MWC 大會上發布，到時候很可能會和 Samsung Galaxy S10以及 Huawei 摺疊屏手機進行競爭。"},{"pid":"08dd0cb714fc9594d2c7224f41bf8082fe191da5","tid":917090,"uid":57424,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"8GB ram 256 GB rom 可以一屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其他機開始10GB RAM 512GB ROM, 永遠係小人20%左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be5c3b3c604b7ccd8db79398d8c60c771b111ba","tid":917090,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"唔差喎個spec, 只要個樣唔好再咁大額頭同下巴，高啲mon ratio, 已經ok"},{"pid":"d461b902c2a477ef7cb1a6076a0a578962be2e20","tid":917090,"uid":35752,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"又係啲on9 FF新聞"},{"pid":"7e770476973cd832a0078dff1e33f7c4b082ca5f","tid":917090,"uid":38472,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"有compact都可以一戰嘅。"},{"pid":"7b8e45e949e3c102ce7d41e8d76d9273e4757814","tid":917090,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"下年小米玩4800萬像鏡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad53282b6f10c6a6a8042dea3d0d662c4a78a59","tid":917090,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"7b8e45e949e3c102ce7d41e8d76d9273e4757814","tid":917090,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"下年小米玩4800萬像鏡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"粒cmos咪就係sony imx586, 人人地買到，作價3000日元，屌米咁都用到，真係當堂令人嚇一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf706fae5d37d797361e1b1541a95c66a476f20","tid":917090,"uid":124017,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7b8e45e949e3c102ce7d41e8d76d9273e4757814","tid":917090,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"下年小米玩4800萬像鏡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:34:59.000Z","ms